    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2011 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8. This naturally aspirated powerplant delivers linear power with a razor-sharp 8,400 RPM redline. The 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission shifts with surgical precision, paired with a variable M differential lock for superior lateral dynamics. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators. The Electronic Damper Control (EDC) provides adjustable damping rates, ensuring the chassis remains composed under high-G loads. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with highway use, the mechanical integrity is excellent, offering a pure visceral experience for the discerning driver.",
